{"id": "ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI", "rating": 4.3, "userRatingCount": 160, "displayName": {"text": "Indigo Cow", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMmJESkRSV3hpUjJWeWFFNXhiMmxDYTJRemFYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We tried the crème brûlée one, and it was fantastic. The caramelized sugar layer on top had that perfect crisp crack, and underneath it was smooth, creamy, and really satisfying. The combination of textures — the crunchy caramelized top with the soft, sweet filling — made every bite really enjoyable.\n\nOverall, it was a great dessert and definitely something I’d order again if I come back. If you like crème brûlée-style desserts with that caramelized sugar shell and creamy base, this one really delivers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We tried the crème brûlée one, and it was fantastic. The caramelized sugar layer on top had that perfect crisp crack, and underneath it was smooth, creamy, and really satisfying. The combination of textures — the crunchy caramelized top with the soft, sweet filling — made every bite really enjoyable.\n\nOverall, it was a great dessert and definitely something I’d order again if I come back. If you like crème brûlée-style desserts with that caramelized sugar shell and creamy base, this one really delivers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lilly B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100283909149072792558/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUolkxhuuhlp_LI9acI3LW6BRJgwcBXW01eNPTaU9D0XDI5PgE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-09T04:14:11.877571938Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMmJESkRSV3hpUjJWeWFFNXhiMmxDYTJRemFYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tnMmJESkRSV3hpUjJWeWFFNXhiMmxDYTJRemFYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70049c741ed:0xe2a0c5ebe5ad07c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM1YxbDRiVFUxY0ZFNWVFVTJUMDlTYUROa2JuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Perfect treat for soft serve lovers on a warm LA day!\n\nInside you’ll find a few seating areas and customer restroom. There’s also some benches outside to chill at. If you’re worried about parking, there’s a 2hr lot behind the building and also street parking!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Perfect treat for soft serve lovers on a warm LA day!\n\nInside you’ll find a few seating areas and customer restroom. There’s also some benches outside to chill at. If you’re worried about parking, there’s a 2hr lot behind the building and also street parking!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hannah Downing", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117354371214569230231/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvMMCsiyb9AQ3TOPaGXhmpCLrhiRf7iy1fDhJnNF6LszmafBcuuA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T01:06:08.404564550Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM1YxbDRiVFUxY0ZFNWVFVTJUMDlTYUROa2JuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM1YxbDRiVFUxY0ZFNWVFVTJUMDlTYUROa2JuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70049c741ed:0xe2a0c5ebe5ad07c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeFprbDVZbU5QU25kRVlXVjRkV2d5UjNCTlNWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Cool place! I really liked the overall vibe. I had the swirl, which combines the milk and matcha flavors. I added chocolate and black sesame/Yuzu sugar toppings.\nIt was pretty good, not something I'd necessarily go back for, but definitely worth trying at least once. Service was fast and friendly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cool place! I really liked the overall vibe. I had the swirl, which combines the milk and matcha flavors. I added chocolate and black sesame/Yuzu sugar toppings.\nIt was pretty good, not something I'd necessarily go back for, but definitely worth trying at least once. Service was fast and friendly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Asli Akal", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104230815839787225596/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiib5MKfXrWh-ywsP0Hvjzdz02qFrVObxcxDR8ffN-DgUl0Kwx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-20T18:13:13.354274435Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeFprbDVZbU5QU25kRVlXVjRkV2d5UjNCTlNWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeFprbDVZbU5QU25kRVlXVjRkV2d5UjNCTlNWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70049c741ed:0xe2a0c5ebe5ad07c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkelpEQkNPVWhUTUVSSGRrVXlVR053YkV0MFpHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I got the Hokkaido Milk flavor + MBR, it was delicious the texture of the mochi was amazing, loved the brown sugar syrup on top. It wasn’t too sweet either, it was like eating like brown sugar boba ice cream in the BEST WAY.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got the Hokkaido Milk flavor + MBR, it was delicious the texture of the mochi was amazing, loved the brown sugar syrup on top. It wasn’t too sweet either, it was like eating like brown sugar boba ice cream in the BEST WAY.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "diya gandhi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112677768893742194188/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV36paemkJg5ycwjHszTsFwwQPSTGOBDVzyJT-oANmslNMa2EyD=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-17T12:39:43.049017216Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkelpEQkNPVWhUTUVSSGRrVXlVR053YkV0MFpHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkelpEQkNPVWhUTUVSSGRrVXlVR053YkV0MFpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c70049c741ed:0xe2a0c5ebe5ad07c6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ7UHHSQDHwoARxget5evFoOI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paUGNWOHlkRVJNUzNacFozaE9ka1owUVRaeFZuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "It was good, but not amazing. I have to preface that the limited edition pumpkin spice brûlée was absolutely delicious and so cute with the powdered sugar pumpkin design. However the ice cream itself was a little icy and missing that gold star quality that I would expect from Hokkaido imported dairy. Overall it was tasty, but not worth the 8 dollar price tag.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was good, but not amazing. I have to preface that the limited edition pumpkin spice brûlée was absolutely delicious and so cute with the powdered sugar pumpkin design. However the ice cream itself was a little icy and missing that gold star quality that I would expect from Hokkaido imported dairy. Overall it was tasty, but not worth the 8 dollar price tag.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alexandra Tran", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111783555571779467964/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjkyGI8G6QHsb5NI6RaPj0WT-AyCHD4c1egC08LI73p0zPy15E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-14T17:22:11.277667939Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paUGNWOHlkRVJNUzNacFozaE9ka1